## gpio-ranges

Specifies the mapping between a GPIO controller and a pin controller. Format: `<pinctrl-phandle pinctrl-base gpio-base count>`.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun50i-h6.dtsi */
pio: pinctrl@300b000 {
    gpio-controller;
    gpio-ranges = <&pio 0 0 256>;
};
```
